":11,"name":"2\u00b0 CAF\u00c9 HIST\u00d3RICO: HOMENAJE A MUJERES SANVICENTINAS QUE HICIERON HISTORIA","body":"En el marco del Mes de la Mujer, la Asociaci\u00f3n Amigos del Museo y de la Historia de San Vicente organiza el 2\u00b0 Caf\u00e9 Hist\u00f3rico, bajo el lema \u201cSin ellas no hay nosotras\u201d, con el objetivo de reconocer a mujeres sanvicentinas que dejaron huella en la comunidad.\r\n\r\nEn esta edici\u00f3n ser\u00e1n homenajeadas:\r\n\ud83d\udd38Julia Ju\u00e1rez \u2013 colchonera y florista\r\n\ud83d\udd38Ma. Enriqueta Catena \u2013 peluquera\r\n\ud83d\udd38\u00c1ngela Girardini \u2013 costurera\r\n\ud83d\udd38Isabel Giussani \u2013 enfermera\r\n\ud83d\udd38Amalia Senor de Macagno  y Serafina Oliva de Macagno \u2013 comerciante (ramos generales)\r\n\r\nPor razones organizativas, se solicita retirar entradas previamente en la Secretar\u00eda del Museo.\r\n\r\nVIERNES 20 \u2013 19:30 HS | AUDITORIO CASA DE LA CULTURA","landmark_id":null,"published_from":"2026-03-16T03:00:00.000000Z","published_to":"2026-03-20T03:00:00.000000Z","active_from":"2026-03-16T03:00:00.000000Z","active_to":"2026-03-20T03:00:00.000000Z","is_important":true,"created_at":"2026-03-17T14:55:29.000000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-17T16:02:33.000000Z","deleted_at":null,"categories":[{"id":2,"name":"Cultura","category_id":null,"external_id":null,"created_at":"2026-02-13T21:38:44.000000Z","updated_at":"2026-02-13T21:38:44.000000Z","pivot":{"categorizable_id":11,"category_id":2,"categorizable_type":"App\\Models\\Event"}}],"landmark":null,"images":[{"id":27,"name":"cafe.jpg","url":"https:\/\/api-sanvicente.vecino.digital\/storage\/images\/6JxRJKfkU2nt2EWeIVX1JPVyrwnaI0tcGjxL4LvK.jpg","path":"images\/6JxRJKfkU2nt2EWeIVX1JPVyrwnaI0tcGjxL4LvK.jpg","type":"image","order":1,"mediable_type":"App\\Models\\Event","mediable_id":11,"created_at":"2026-03-17T14:55:29.000000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-17T14:55:29.000000Z"}],"links":[],"sounds":[],"videos":[]},{"id":14,"name":"ACTO D\u00cdA DE LA MEMORIA PO